Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesan pertamaku,\Ndia tampak seperti bocah laki-laki biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.51,0:00:24.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,berbeda dari bocah kekanakan\Nyang tak kusukai.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putri Kathyln?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.21,0:02:01.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pangeran Curtis?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.91,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ada keributan apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.18,0:02:11.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang Mulia, saat kami sedang\Nbersenang-senang,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.85,0:02:15.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,rakyat jelata ini memukul kami\Ntanpa alasan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya bicara begitu. Padahal...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kami tak berbuat apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.58,0:02:26.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah melukai Dwarf seperti ini,\Nkau masih merasa punya alasan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa benar begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, kami cuma membela diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.75,0:02:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal sudah jelas itu bohong,\Ndasar Kakak bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh kebodohan tingkat tinggi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.31,0:02:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itukah ucapanmu di hadapan\Npangeran Kerajaan Sapin?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya mohon maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.35,0:02:50.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulut saya kerap kasar\Nsaat mendengar kebohongan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana bisa anak sekecil ini\Npunya kekuatan sebesar itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong maafkan keponakan saya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia hanya ingin bilang\Nbahwa mereka berbohong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.82,0:03:06.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Helstea, sedang apa di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.20,0:03:10.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami kebetulan lewat saat mereka\Nmenindas anak ini beramai-ramai.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berani-beraninya kalian membohongiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebutkan nama kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama saya Jamiel.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya putra sulung\NKeluarga Tridant, Pangeran.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga Tridant?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini jadi merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.35,0:03:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga Tridant penyumbang besar\Nbagi kerajaan dan Akademi Xyrus.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika mereka tahu penerusnya celaka...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tindak kekerasan yang kalian lakukan...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang paling penting,\Ntak ada yang terluka parah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, jika kalian setuju\Nmenganggap ini selesai...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.65,0:03:53.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekalipun keluarga kerajaan,\Ndia pasti tak akan berani.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman Vincent membawa\Ngulungan komunikasi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku membawanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau menghubungi siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cynthia Goodsky.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia sudah gila?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memanggil Ketua Akademi Xyrus?\NItu tak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.41,0:04:16.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Vincent?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.21,0:04:21.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau membuatku repot,\Nmemanggilku tiba-tiba begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini Arthur Leywin.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.90,0:04:28.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau yang memanggil,\Nkapan pun aku senang menerimanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah lama sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?\NKenapa mendadak begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.41,0:04:38.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jamiel Tridant dan temannya\Ndari Akademi Xyrus
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.15,0:04:41.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyalahgunakan kuasa\Natas seorang Dwarf karena prasangka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya ingin Anda mengeluarkan\Nmereka dari akademi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan kau ini, tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang Tridant?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal yang satu itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedekat apa pun Ketua\Ndengan rakyat jelata itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,mengingat besarnya sumbangan\Nkeluargaku pada akademi,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,mustahil dia membelamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Anda masih ingin saya masuk akademi...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, akan kukeluarkan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin kau memaafkan sikapku tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.81,0:05:24.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak teguh memegang pendirian\Nbukanlah sikap pantas bagi pangeran.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.71,0:05:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya juga ingin minta maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya tak mampu menahan emosi saya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajar saja kau marah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasialisme tak punya tempat di benua ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak pertama bertemu juga begini...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.73,0:05:50.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak mendengarkanku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah kau minum teh bersamaku kapan-kapan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.18,0:06:08.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, sampai jumpa lagi di akademi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi itu apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.01,0:06:21.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itukah adikku yang kejam\Ndan tak berperasaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memang berbeda dari yang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manusia, Elf, dan Dwarf,\Npara hadirin sekalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.37,0:06:39.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku Blaine Glayder, Raja Kerajaan Sapin.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini berkumpul raja dan ratu\Ndari ketiga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita berkumpul di hari perayaan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.88,0:06:51.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian semua paham permusuhan\Nantara Elf dan Manusia, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.89,0:06:56.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Juga bahwa Dwarf hanya dianggap\Nsebatas rekan bisnis.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, buanglah masa lalu\Ndan prasangka itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pandanglah segala hal\Ndari sudut yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan hanya demi diri sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.98,0:07:13.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,melainkan demi anak-anak\Ndan masa depan benua ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.58,0:07:25.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya, semua akan tahu adanya\Nbenua lain selain Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.21,0:07:31.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang dikhawatirkan, benua baru itu\Nmengirim Mana Beast penyamar
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk mengawasi Benua Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.91,0:07:39.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bukan karena takut,\Nmereka berbuat begitu
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.05,0:07:41.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin memang berniat jahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Arthur?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau di sini, tapi pikiranmu entah ke mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya mendukung penuh gagasan luar biasa
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.58,0:08:00.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang Raja Glayder paparkan\Nsoal masa depan benua kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di tanah air kita, Benua Dicathen,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada tempat berbahaya\Nyang tak seorang pun berani menjejakinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.11,0:08:11.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, jika ada misteri dan bahaya\Nyang jauh lebih besar
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,di luar benua, apa jadinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.93,0:08:19.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadirin sekalian, hari ini kami nyatakan,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,ditemukan bukti adanya benua lain
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,selain Benua Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang kita ketahui sejauh ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka berusaha menjalin kontak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, untuk saat ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita belum punya teknologi\Nuntuk perjalanan jauh ke benua lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.65,0:08:47.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita semua makhluk yang lahir\Ndi benua sama, Benua Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bangga akan hal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.51,0:08:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pun berharap generasi mendatang\Nmerasa demikian.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.15,0:08:58.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini menandai awal era baru
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagi tanah air, benua ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.23,0:09:12.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin amat sulit menyatukan\Ntiga ras dan tiga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.74,0:09:17.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami ingin memberi tugas\Nkepada enam orang di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.18,0:09:24.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka yang paling berani dan cerdas\Ndari tiap kerajaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.58,0:09:29.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka mengemban kepercayaan\Ndari keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.25,0:09:34.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Agar kami dan seluruh rakyat\Nbisa menyambut era baru,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.31,0:09:37.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,keenam orang ini akan berjuang menjaga\Nkeamanan dan kemakmuran tanah air.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai sekarang, mereka adalah
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.81,0:09:46.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Six Lance, enam tombak\Nyang jadi simbol benua ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alea Triscan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Varay Aurae.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Olfred Warend.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aya Grephin.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mica Earthborn.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bairon Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi itu Keluarga Wykes?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tak salah, Lucas juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Six Lance,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,lindungilah dan berilah kami kehormatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagi kalian yang kini berusaha\Nmenjadi penyihir kelak,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,berjuanglah agar bisa\Nmenjadi salah satu Six Lance.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebab kemungkinan itu tak terbatas.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.45,0:10:42.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari itu, menjadi alasanku\Nmenghadapi kenyataan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucas Wykes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat mengantar rekannya menuju kematian,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.98,0:10:50.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia lari dari dosanya menggunakan kuasa\Ndan koneksi orang tuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.41,0:10:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka memperingatkanku bahwa balas dendam\Npada Lucas sama saja dengan bunuh diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.81,0:10:59.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata maksudnya adalah sosok kakaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.51,0:11:03.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakaknya bukan sekadar penyihir yang kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia salah satu dari Lance.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih penting dari balas dendam pada Lucas,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada hal lain yang harus kulakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore, ayo, ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam ini, kau tunggu di kamar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.38,0:11:28.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman Vincent mewanti-wanti,\Nbisa saja ada orang mencurigakan masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak ingin membuatmu dalam bahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kusuruh seseorang\Nmembawakan banyak makanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asyik!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang, silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.05,0:11:48.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti, ajaklah dia berdansa.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, aku akan masuk\Nke Akademi Xyrus.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah kau pergi minum denganku?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Logam ini kubuat sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau berkenan...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rambut hitammu indah sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.25,0:12:12.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia benar-benar ingin punya pacar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, waktunya tokoh utama muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah pesta ini\Nhanya mengundang keluarga?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat ulang tahun, Eleanor!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin berterima kasih\Nkepada kalian semua.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah datang
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.92,0:12:53.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,merayakan ulang tahun putri kesayanganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.50,0:12:59.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai hari ini,\Naku menjalani hidup bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.18,0:13:02.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harapan terbesarku adalah putra dan putriku
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,berdansa bersama untuk pertama kalinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.05,0:13:05.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.81,0:13:09.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak tahu mereka berdua akan berdansa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak kapan mereka berlatih?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka tak berlatih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar Reynolds!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau, aku tidak bisa berdansa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eleanor.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah kau berdansa denganku?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musik dimulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka sudah berlatih, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.05,0:14:35.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dansa yang kupelajari\Ndi kehidupan sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak kusangka berguna sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dansamu bagus, Eleanor.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus sampai bikin aku kesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa kita bicara?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini, aku ingin minum,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku tahan dengan jus saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bergaya keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ada perlu apa
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,peneliti terbaik di benua kali ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sindiranmu tajam sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.88,0:15:07.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Desain revisimu sudah disetujui\Ndewan penasihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.18,0:15:10.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang memberi tahu\Nbahwa kapalnya mulai dibuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewan penasihat?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Organisasi yang dibentuk\Nsebagai forum bagi raja dan ratu
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk membahas berbagai masalah\Nsecara setara di Benua Dicathen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti kau dapat hadiah hebat\Nberkat desain itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Uang? Popularitas? Kekuasaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.18,0:15:31.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua itu hanya alat untuk mencapai hasil.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang sungguh kuinginkan adalah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu, permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda Profesor Gideon, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami lihat Anda di berita.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda yang merancang kapal raksasa...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Benar energinya tanpa mana?\N- Aku sedang sibuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Bakar sesuatu jadi penggerak?\N- Arthur, aku belum...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Popularitas itu
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,menuntut pengorbanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.\NTernyata kau ada di sini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya kau sibuk\Nkarena jadi anggota Dewan Siswa.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku baru saja pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lama tak jumpa, ya, Lilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, benar-benar sudah lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau setinggi ini sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.46,0:16:25.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Melihat banyaknya pria\Nyang tertarik padamu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,di sekolah pun kau populer, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak punya kekasih atau semacamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.10,0:16:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, hidupku berubah\Nberkat dirimu juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau bilang begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang jadi pacarmu harus orang\Nyang kuakui dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penilaianku ketat\Nseperti Paman Vincent, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arthur menganggapku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.36,0:16:53.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ehm.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi, Nona.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.51,0:16:59.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, boleh kupinjam pemuda\Ndi sana sebentar saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Profesor Gideon?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.51,0:17:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, sampai nanti ya, Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.35,0:17:12.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang aku orang terkenal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Merendahlah sedikit.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau populer sekali di kalangan wanita, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gadis tadi itu menyukaimu, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kulihat kalian cocok.\NApa kau tak berniat mengambil langkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaannya padaku
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukanlah cinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.18,0:17:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih dekat ke rasa terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia belum menyadarinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dia pasti bisa membedakannya\Nsaat waktunya tiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.85,0:17:42.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesal juga, kau sudah terbiasa\Nmembahas hal seperti ini di usiamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.65,0:17:46.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ke sini\Nbukan mau tanya soal asmara, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.19,0:17:49.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh ya, yang tadi mau kukatakan,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.41,0:17:53.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan uang, popularitas, dan kuasa\Ndari dewan penasihat,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku ingin mendapatkan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengetahuanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.65,0:18:09.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah menyesal\Nsekadar menyerahkan desain mesin uap.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.85,0:18:15.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau berbuat hal\Nyang mengubah dunia lebih jauh lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benua ini baik-baik saja\Ntanpa campur tanganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.83,0:18:26.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, benar kau masih punya\Npenemuan pengubah dunia, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.85,0:18:27.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.61,0:18:31.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku jadi bersemangat.\N- Dia cuma dengar yang ingin dia dengar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Gideon.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.84,0:18:39.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kutegaskan,\Naku tak berniat memuaskan rasa ingin tahumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tersadar dari mabuk\Nmendengar ucapanmu tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nbagaimana kalau saling memberi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.10,0:18:54.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan minta penemuan pengubah dunia,\Ncukup pendapatmu sesekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.61,0:18:58.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai gantinya,\Nakan kusediakan apa pun yang kau butuhkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sepakat?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah ini terlihat cantik?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaun lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya di sini juga ada hadiah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini hadiah dari siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.05,0:19:39.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada surat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eleanor tersayang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.81,0:19:45.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mulai bosan dengan banyaknya\Ngaun dan peralatan teh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Busur?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Busur yang indah sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Desainnya seperti milik Elf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak tertera siapa pengirimnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah mungkin...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.05,0:20:08.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak apa kau cuma menyerahkan\Nhadiah tanpa menemuinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.15,0:20:12.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini, biar Arthur\Nmemikirkan adiknya saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.58,0:20:16.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham.\NMenyapa keluarga orang yang kita suka
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,butuh keberanian, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau tak mau diganggu\Nsaat berjumpa lagi dengannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang, bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan segera
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,bertemu Arthur di akademi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana hadiah dari sang kakak tersayang?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eleanor, hadiahnya sudah cukup, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu juga dapat?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebuah kalung!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.60,0:20:57.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kalung itu, kalian terlindungi\Nmeski aku dan Ayah tak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlihat cantik.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana itu dijual?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.21,0:21:06.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali,\Nkalung itu hanya ada dua di dunia.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat ulang tahun, Eleanor.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka yang berharga bagiku.
